description: The kimonolabs World Cup 2014 API provides easy access to up-to-date player, team and match data for the 2014 World Cup as well as historical player performance across their respective club teams. The API is RESTful and uses standard HTTP response codes to indicate errors. JSON will be returned in all responses from the API.
